trans-unit.source: Specifies the status of a workflow instance.

The following code example demonstrates how you can use the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowStatus> values to set the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions.WorkflowStatus%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 다음 코드 예제에서는 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowStatus> 값을 사용하여 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions.WorkflowStatus%2A> 속성을 설정하는 방법을 보여 줍니다.

trans-unit.source: Each value constrains the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> in a different way.
This code example is part of the Workflow Monitor SDK Sample from the DatabaseService.cs file.
trans-unit.target: 이 코드 예제는 DatabaseService.cs 파일에 있는 Workflow Monitor SDK 샘플의 일부입니다.

trans-unit.source: The workflow instance has been created by a call to one of the overloaded <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.CreateWorkflow(System.Type)" /> methods.
trans-unit.target: 워크플로 인스턴스가 오버로드된 <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowRuntime.CreateWorkflow(System.Type)" /> 메서드 중 하나를 호출하여 만들어졌습니다.

trans-unit.source: The workflow instance has been suspended by a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.SuspendActivity" /> activity, by a call to <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.Suspend(System.String)" />,or by the workflow runtime engine.
trans-unit.target: 워크플로 인스턴스가 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.SuspendActivity" /> 활동, <see cref="M:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.Suspend(System.String)" /> 호출 또는 워크플로 런타임 엔진에 의해 일시 중단되었습니다.

trans-unit.source: The workflow instance has been terminated by a

<xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.TerminateActivity> activity, by a call to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.Terminate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, or by the workflow runtime engine.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.TerminateActivity> 활동, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.Terminate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 호출 또는 워크플로 런타임 엔진에 의해 종료되었습니다.
